{"tid":632621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近兩周收血量欠佳 紅十字會將推手機Apps預約捐血","createTime":"2018-04-17T14:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T15:14:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e24bb9a5ea78ab9423b78b186ddf549237ca5475","tid":632621,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"紅十字會輸血服務中心上月初擴展網上預約服務至所有捐血站，中心副顧問醫生梁雅詩稱，截至3月底逾400人透過網上預約登記捐血，當中約120至130人已成功捐血。她透露，稍後該中心會推出手機應用程式，屆時可透過手機預約，期望有預約者由到達捐血站起計，約半小時可完成捐血。<br />\n<br />\n梁雅詩說，近兩星期收血量不太理想，每日平均僅700至800人登記，幸現時血庫水平仍然穩定，但她強調應未雨綢繆。<br />\n該中心上周五及昨日在政府總部舉行捐血活動，共120名公務員捐血。中心行政及醫務總監李卓廣指，期望今次與政府部門合作的行動可起示範作用，鼓勵更多市民踴躍捐血，為全港醫院的病人提供穩定血液供應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180417/58085992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F58085992&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iL8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=22aa6ef4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F58085992&h=b8ed4716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180417/58085992</a>"},{"pid":"c4a15a8cc53ea51dd5b0aff4666aa5df850d7554","tid":632621,"uid":156751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:36:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4fdeb7c75ff3c34ed939a92f8baadd02f7c7c9","tid":632621,"uid":8949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:56:41.000Z","msg":"我淨係預約"},{"pid":"384da821967f31d54e8e6fbf9ec242b759f8787a","tid":632621,"uid":62950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:05:12.000Z","msg":"你有得預約星期一至五夜晚八點後再算啦<br />\n<br />\n咪撚到時裝完個app <br />\n好似我的天文台唔記得熄提示 每20分鐘提我有陣風咁 <br />\n提我血庫不足呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f485887f42d3fb8c9edb1ca3743cf4321e354474","tid":632621,"uid":135767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73bf794724bed6be655f09a8066b17469c92de0b","tid":632621,"uid":176166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}